      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, but my doctor is super hard to get a hold of and it's been hurting all morning. i've taken ibuprofen before when i wasn't on the warfarin and it worked fine. surely a couple of pills won't make a huge difference right? i just really need the pain to stop so i can focus.",
